OL,3,CEngland cricketer Graham Thorpe took
OL,4,Chis own life, family confirms
OL,6,FFormer England batter Graham Thorpe
OL,7,Ftook his own life, aged 55, after
OL,8,Fstruggling with depression and anxiety
OL,9,Ffor the last couple of years, his wife
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe England and Wales Cricket Board
OL,13,Fannounced his death last Monday.
OL,15,FHis mental health "led him to make a
OL,16,Fserious attempt on his life in May
OL,17,F2022, which resulted in a prolonged
OL,18,Fstay in an intensive care unit,"
OL,19,FAmanda Thorpe, Graham's wife, said in
OL,20,Fan interview with former England
OL,21,Fcricketer Mike Atherton, for The Times.
