OL,6,F"Despite glimpses of hope and of the
OL,7,Fold Graham, he continued to suffer
OL,8,Ffrom depression and anxiety, which at
OL,9,Ftimes got very severe. We supported
OL,10,Fhim as a family and he tried many,
OL,11,Fmany treatments but unfortunately none
OL,12,Fof them really seemed to work."
OL,14,FMrs Thorpe said he was "renowned as
OL,15,Fsomeone who was very mentally strong
OL,16,Fon the field and he was in good
OL,17,Fphysical health".
OL,19,F"But mental illness is a real disease
OL,20,Fand can affect anyone," she added.
