OL,3,CEngland cricketer Graham Thorpe took
OL,4,Chis own life, family confirms
OL,6,F"Despite having a wife and two
OL,7,Fdaughters whom he loved and who loved
OL,8,Fhim, he did not get better.
OL,10,F"He was so unwell in recent times and
OL,11,Fhe really did believe that we would be
OL,12,Fbetter off without him and we are
OL,13,Fdevastated that he acted on that and
OL,14,Ftook his own life."
OL,16,FHis 22-year-old daughter, Kitty
OL,17,FThorpe, said it was "heartbreaking to
OL,18,Fsee how withdrawn" her father had
OL,19,Fbecome following his mental health
OL,20,Fstruggles.
