OL,6,F"He was not the same person," she
OL,7,Fsaid. "It was strange to see this
OL,8,Fperson trapped in the body of Dad."
OL,10,F"We are not ashamed of talking about
OL,11,Fit," she said.
OL,13,F"There is nothing to hide and it is
OL,14,Fnot a stigma. We were trying to help
OL,15,Fhim get better before and trying to
OL,16,Fprotect him, which is why we said
OL,17,Fnothing. This is the time now to share
OL,18,Fthe news, however horrible it is."
