OL,11,FThorpe won 100 Test caps during a
OL,12,Fstellar England career and was
OL,13,Fregarded as one of the best batters of
OL,14,Fhis generation, with his international
OL,15,Fexploits running alongside a 17-year
OL,16,Fspell with his county side Surrey.
OL,18,FHe made his international debut in
OL,19,F1993 and scored a century on his first
OL,20,FAshes appearance, becoming the first
OL,21,FEngland player to do so in 20 years.
